{"tid":329200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係學校同條死mk隻揪","createTime":"2017-07-20T07:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T15:53:58.000Z","uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"512058be9bae5dfb803c16f311e72fc1bdce2046","tid":329200,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:31:03.000Z","msg":"依加我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好拎好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒拎FD 嚇拎到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後個訓導主任去籃球場打到我地HiHi, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"70b795a96907dde6dee4dd4629b99752ed9f68c5","tid":329200,"uid":83819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"咁 邊條mk 輸左"},{"pid":"a229f94cc7380536c32fa6962825789c25d6add2","tid":329200,"uid":42392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204f0686c06aa026b425769f851f04f73d48d402","tid":329200,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁 邊條mk 輸左</blockquote><br />\n大家都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a723051e3f5047642f251d827d7e97013e1f9c7","tid":329200,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"我d肌肉簡直完美"},{"pid":"1752bf2aa852209c5b07a90edcc765b3802d0342","tid":329200,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"呢篇好似好少回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6fa17a179b533a9479